author: Brian
title: The Golden State Warriors are getting roasted for another cheesy photoshoot
text:
Feb 16, 2017 at 10:26p ET 0Shares 
The Golden State Warriors launched a thousand Twitter jokes last season with an incredibly lame photoshoot straight out of a department store catalog â€” and the internet was back at it again on Thursday night with a fresh batch of Dubs photos. 
At least it wasn't their fault this time, though, as it appears Stephen Curry, Klay Thompson, Kevin Durant and Draymond Green posed for a routine NBA All-Star photoshoot. Yet that didn't stop Twitter from firing off quips, Photoshops and after-school-special Public Service Announcements at the expense of Golden State's four All-Stars. 
Here are a few of our favorites. 021617-NBA-Warriors-Roast-13
